{"pageProps":{"article":{"id":"650facbacb","title":"对两报一刊元旦社论稿《迎接无产阶级文化大革命的全面胜利的批语","origin":"","is_range_date":false,"dates":[{"id":"9f9dd83b59","index":0,"year":1967,"month":12,"day":29,"articleId":"650facbacb"}],"tags":[{"id":"9bc2c334c7","name":"批示","type":"文稿类型"},{"id":"dd2b275f6c","name":"毛泽东","type":"人物"}],"aliases":[],"publications":[{"id":"maoquanji50","name":"毛泽东全集第50卷","internal":false,"official":false,"type":"pdf","author":"张迪杰","files":"https://raw.githubusercontent.com/banned-historical-archives/banned-historical-archives0/main/mao-quanji/50-OCR.pdf"}],"authors":[{"id":"261e5467ec","name":"毛泽东"}]},"publication_details":{"maoquanji50":{"comments":[{"id":"c97750ce60","publicationId":"maoquanji50","articleId":"650facbacb","index":1,"part_index":-99,"offset":-99,"text":"姚文元，当时任中共中央文化革命小组组员。1967年12月28日，他把《人民日报》、《红旗》杂志、《解放军报》1968年元旦社论稿《迎接无产阶级文化大革命的全面胜利》送毛泽东审阅时写道：“元旦社论，已经碰头会讨论通过（谈了两次），现送上，是否妥当，请审阅批示！这篇社论在1968年1月1日两报一刊发表。"},{"id":"7a7f1c88aa","publicationId":"maoquanji50","articleId":"650facbacb","index":2,"part_index":-99,"offset":-99,"text":"在姚文元送审的社论稿上，毛泽东删去了“东心祝愿我们的伟大导师、世界人民心中的红太阳毛主席方寿无疆！万寿无疆！”一句中“世界人民心中的红太阳”和后一个“万寿无疆”，删去了“用当代最高水平的马克思列宁主义——毛泽东思想武装起来的中国共产党”一句中“最高水平的”五个字。"}],"contents":[{"id":"c8afb4fbb8","type":"title","text":"对两报一刊元旦社论稿《迎接无产阶级文化大革命的全面胜利》的批语","index":0,"publicationId":"maoquanji50","articleId":"650facbacb"},{"id":"c97750ce60","type":"paragraph","text":"姚文元同志：","index":1,"publicationId":"maoquanji50","articleId":"650facbacb"},{"id":"7a7f1c88aa","type":"paragraph","text":"看了一遍，觉得可用。去掉了几个浮夸的形容词，请你们豹定。","index":2,"publicationId":"maoquanji50","articleId":"650facbacb"},{"id":"633fc6093d","type":"paragraph","text":"毛泽东","index":3,"publicationId":"maoquanji50","articleId":"650facbacb"},{"id":"92e143a77f","type":"paragraph","text":"十二月廿九日上午四时","index":4,"publicationId":"maoquanji50","articleId":"650facbacb"}],"page":{"id":"d29d4b3cc2","publicationId":"maoquanji50","articleId":"650facbacb","start":168,"end":168}}}},"__N_SSG":true}